    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
